<title type="html"><![CDATA[3/17 (Thu)Investment scammers on social media ran off with $285M 2021 / Taiwanese should prepare to reopen (Host: Joyce)]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/viewtopic.php?t=599&amp;p=622#p622"><![CDATA[
Investment scammers on social media ran off with $285M in 2021 / Taiwanese should prepare to reopen (Host: Joyce)<br /><br />Agenda:<br />7:00-7:05 pm Opening Remarks<br />7:05-7:40 pm Session 1: Group Discussion<br />7:40-8:00 pm Individual Presentation<br />8:00-8:05 pm Break<br />8:05-8:40: Session 2: Group Discussion<br />8:40-9:00 pm Individual Presentation<br /><br />We will hold a zoom meeting only.<br /><br />Zoom meeting: Please click the link below<br /><br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw">https://zoomtw.zoom.us/j/92987266213?pw</a><!-- m --> ...<br />Meeting ID:929 8726 6213<br />Password:112233<br /><br />Session I:<br />Investment scammers on social media ran off with $285M in 2021<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.nbcnews.com/business/investment-scammers-social-media-ran-285-million-2021-rcna14279">https://www.nbcnews.com/business/invest ... -rcna14279</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Questions<br />1.Why do scammers target us on social media now more than ever?<br />2.Have you been scammed on social media? How to protect ourselves from social media scams?<br />3.People younger than 50 were more than twice as likely as older adults to report losing money to these scams . Do you know what the reason is?<br />4.How to spot a social media scam? If you see or experience scam on social media, how should you do?<br /><br />Session II:<br />Taiwanese should prepare to reopen<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="https://www.taipeitimes.com/News/editorials/archives/2022/03/06/2003774259">https://www.taipeitimes.com/News/editor ... 2003774259</a><!-- m --><br /><br />1.Are we nearing the end of the COVID-19 pandemic? When will the COVID-19 pandemic end?<br />2.Studies have shown the antiviral pill led to a nearly 90% reduction in hospitalizations and deaths among patients most likely to get severe disease. Do you think antiviral pills might be humanity’s best hope to eventually end the Covid pandemic?<br />3.Europe and North America are open to quarantine-free travel for those who are vaccinated. Do you dare to take a trip to those countries?<br />4.Do you think Taiwan should further relax border restrictions and reintroduce tourism?...<br /><br />P.S.<br />1.參加三次(含實體及線上會議)後，只要繳交1,000元(學生500元)，即可成為ROYAL終身會員!<br />2.請帶著開放的心與熱情來參加全英文會話聚會!<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.royalclub.tw/bbs3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=38674">Louie Wang</a> — Fri Mar 11, 2022 10:08 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
